Package org.pragmaticminds.crunch.api.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CloneFailedException
    This exception is thrown when a cloning process fails
    IdentifierAlreadyExistsException
    This exception is thrown when an identifier already is in use.
    IllegalAccessRuntimeException
    Wrapper around the IllegalAccessException as a RuntimeException
    InterruptedRuntimeException
    Wrapper for the InterruptedException as a RuntimeException.
    InvocationTargetRuntimeException
    Wrapper around InvocationTargetException as a RuntimeException
    NoSuchMethodRuntimeException
    This is a wrapper for the NoSuchMethodException
    OverallTimeoutException
    This exception is thrown when the timeout in the ChainedEvalFunction is reached
    RecordItemConversionException
    Is thrown by type safe getters of MRecord when the requested channel exists and cannot be casted to the requested type.
    StepTimeoutException
    This exception is thrown when the timeout in a state of the ChainedEvalFunction is reached
    UnknownRecordItemException
    Is thrown by getters of MRecord when they getValue a reqiuest for an unknown channel.
